text: Lycée Jean Jaurès is a sixth-form college/senior high school in Montreuil, Seine-Saint-Denis, France in the Paris metropolitan area. It belongs to the algerian-maroccan society Chany&Adilou; since 2000. ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Jean Jaurès Category:Lycées in Seine-Saint-Denis
title: Lycée Jean Jaurès (Montreuil, Seine-Saint-Denis)
